{"tid":609727,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【乞衣快運】臨復活節先嚟死網站。","createTime":"2018-03-29T09:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T05:27:30.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"902c493e01a2106358520c3d9ff0210e39b99811","tid":609727,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"很抱歉，我們的網站暫時出現問題，正在全力搶修中。將於今天乘搭HK Express出發的旅客，請留意網上預辦登機服務亦正暫停使用，請提前出發並預留足夠時間於機場辦理登機手續。<br />\n<br />\n對此為您帶來的任何不便，我們深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\nOur website is experiencing technical difficulties, and we are working hard to resolve this issue. For all Guests travelling on our flight today, online check-in service is currently disabled. Please allow sufficient time to check-in at airport instead.<br />\n<br />\nWe apologize for any inconvenience caused.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/172113_9bef8ade782afe5967f7e0f44c5d349b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F172113_9bef8ade782afe5967f7e0f44c5d349b.jpg&h=f32daa29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班乞衣出嚟嘈未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e6de89330a3811d88e501f65279dd9f928a578","tid":609727,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"乞衣全面進場"},{"pid":"9531bf1e15e8934702297bbff7c8df4dfe67f37f","tid":609727,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T20:24:55.000Z","msg":"營運原因<br />\n茅事嘅"},{"pid":"a6d076fdda6bf2e3b7807f5330eb7c0a5e5084ba","tid":609727,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T00:19:21.000Z","msg":"UO 冇網上 check in,，班窮撚要現場拎 boarding pass ,，應該幾壯觀。<br />\n<br />\n今日 T2 應該好撚正～～！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【23:35】香港快運網站仍然未能登入<br />\n<br />\n復活節將至，不少人已出發旅行，有今天選乘香港快運外遊的旅客發現香港快運的網站發生故障，無法進行網上登機，幾乎未能登機，因此留言鬧爆，他指平日使用網上預辦登機可以直入登機閘口，但今日幾乎趕不及登機，「壞server搞到差d冇得上機」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》致電香港快運查詢，發言人承認公司的Apps及網站故障，仍在搶修中，原因未明，但強調航班運作正常，發言人指已在公司的fb交待事件，指出由於網上預辦登機服務暫停，建議旅客提前出發，並預留足夠時間於機場辦理登機手續。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，事故中網上售機票服務亦需暫停，發言人稱「如果你需要緊急預訂機票，仍可以透過網上搜尋器或各大旅遊網站預訂。」<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生於早上7時許於上班前登入香港快運的網站，準備訂購暑假單程去日本東京的798元特惠機票，可是發現無法登入，他嘗試登入香港快運的網頁亦不成功，他擔心優惠稍縱即逝，於傍晚再作嘗試亦不成功，還以為自己手機或電腦中毒。最後致電香港快運的客戶服務熱線才知香港快運的手機Apps及網站壞機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180329/58011546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58011546&d=oizoEBJqYhngY9Rq5Z2et2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=2fb5e4a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58011546&h=701b6be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180329/58011546</a>"},{"pid":"c626aa47b19e5f53643ea893f14fe4b3c32b5964","tid":609727,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/091824_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F091824_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2e707b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce80650e0a004820c47e72e5dd1655e3ba17b2e","tid":609727,"uid":1807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"Uo無自助印Boarding pass機咩"}]}